com.hms_networks.americas.sc.taginfo

Class TagInfoManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.hms_networks.americas.sc.taginfo.TagInfoManager

  • public class TagInfoManager
extends java.lang.Object
    Class that allows the retrieval of tag information of an Ewon Flexy by generating an export block descriptor call and parsing the response to store as a list of TagInfo objects.
    Since:
    1.0
    Author:
    HMS Networks, MU Americas Solution Center

      • applyHistoricalLogRateForTagGroup

        public static void applyHistoricalLogRateForTagGroup(TagGroup tagGroup,
                                                     java.lang.String logInterval)
                                              throws com.ewon.ewonitf.EWException,
                                                     java.lang.InterruptedException
        Applies the specified historical log interval to tags in the specified tag group. To reduce the time waiting for this method to return, it is recommended that this method be called from a new Thread.
        Parameters:
        tagGroup - tag group to modify
        logInterval - new historical log interval
        Throws:
        com.ewon.ewonitf.EWException - if unable to apply historical log interval
        java.lang.InterruptedException - if unable to sleep between updating tags
